<section class="section process-section" id="process">
  <div class="section-inner">
    <div class="sec-tag">Placement Methodology</div>
    <h2 class="sec-title">From Profile to <em>Deployment</em></h2>
    <p class="sec-desc">A disciplined six-stage mobilisation process â€” designed to protect the worker, satisfy the employer, and comply fully with bilateral labour regulations.</p>
    <div class="process-track">
      <div class="pstep reveal">
        <div class="pstep-num">01</div>
        <h5>Profile Registration</h5>
        <p>Free skill documentation, qualification verification, and biometric registration. No fees at this stage.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="pstep reveal">
        <div class="pstep-num">02</div>
        <h5>Skill Screening</h5>
        <p>Trade test, aptitude evaluation, and physical fitness assessment aligned to destination country standards.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="pstep reveal">
        <div class="pstep-num">03</div>
        <h5>Employer Matching</h5>
        <p>Profile presented to verified employer network. Demand letters secured. Interview coordination arranged.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="pstep reveal">
        <div class="pstep-num">04</div>
        <h5>Documentation</h5>
        <p>Visa documentation, attestation, medical examination, insurance, and emigration clearance â€” fully managed.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="pstep reveal">
        <div class="pstep-num">05</div>
        <h5>Pre-Departure Orientation</h5>
        <p>Cultural briefing, labour rights training, emergency contacts, and contract review in the candidate's language.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="pstep reveal">
        <div class="pstep-num">06</div>
        <h5>Deployment &amp; Support</h5>
        <p>Airport assistance, employer reception coordination, and post-arrival welfare follow-up through the first 90 days.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

